	* lib/getdef.c: SHA_CRYPT_MAX_ROUNDS and SHA_CRYPT_MIN_ROUNDS can
	only exist if configured with --with-sha-crypt.
	* man/login.defs.d/SHA_CRYPT_MIN_ROUNDS.xml: Likewise.

