	* man/expiry.1.xml: Does not use any login.defs parameter.
	* man/gpasswd.1.xml: Uses ENCRYPT_METHOD, MAX_MEMBERS_PER_GROUP,
	MD5_CRYPT_ENAB, SHA_CRYPT_MIN_ROUNDS.
