	fixed inactive/mindays/warndays/maxdays overflow (similar to RH#198920).

	* src/groupadd.c, src/groupmod.c:
	fixed GID overflow (fixed http://bugzilla.redhat.com/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=198920).

